Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_int_info1

This register contains the second header word of the illegal s2m transaction associated with the SLI_ERR interrupt. The remaining information is located in SRIO()_INT_INFO0. This register is only updated when the SLI_ERR is initially detected. Once the interrupt is cleared then additional information can be captured.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
